{"tid":1440110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔 路 指 引","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T03:59:46.000Z","uid":23707,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"409d857df09bfe6dfd140876ef036f0f18f85345","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"以下講嘢會有人覺得唔順耳<br />\n因為我會話佔路要比啲車有路走<br />\n不過咁多人鐘意講唔好失民意<br />\n以下就係可以消耗狗力同不失民意嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1W0Det.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1W0Det.png&h=e74c9a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以而家大圍嘅情況做例子<br />\n迴該處一block<br />\nABCD四個位就會塞哂車<br />\n呢個時候要做嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去後面一個路口圖中橙線block路<br />\n等後面嘅車唔好塞入嚟<br />\n然後再協助塞喺ABCD路段嘅車離開</span><br />\n<br />\n咁嘅方式一來佔到路<br />\n二來可以令無辜車輛走到<br />\n因為啲車塞喺度其實無意義<br />\n只會有人出嚟屌鳩義士<br />\n比佢哋有得走<br />\n佢哋條氣會順啲 <br />\n所謂民意亦唔會被影響<br />\n<br />\n完成之後<br />\n鐘意守又得<br />\nbe water去第二個位又得<br />\n無得輸"},{"pid":"1cfc108bb40c12f6187c0d6fc929a922a8c4703f","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"12e9f73c44fe54806e4259164d390be0c49842b5","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7aaa0c0b16fbfc7c28e40b94f33b3023df037629","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a67feafb156bd777230e37f15ab1b5795a9267fe","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f19b6f99cc651064963c92128d8d8dfafeb9962b","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d2e97fdc44bab812704d01d8ed94c7b164e58333","tid":1440110,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:50:24.000Z"